data.name: grdScPost_modifier.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.SUSIK_CODE , A.SUSIK_NAME , A.SUSIK_NAME_GANA , A.SUSIK_DETAIL_GUBUN FROM CHT0115 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.SUSIK_DETAIL_GUBUN = :f_susik_detail_gubun AND ( A.SUSIK_NAME LIKE '%'||:f_susik_name||'%' OR A.SUSIK_NAME_GANA LIKE '%'||:f_susik_name||'%' ) AND NVL(A.SUSIK_DISABLE_DATE, TO_DATE('99991231', 'YYYYMMDD')) >= TRUNC(SYSDATE) ORDER BY A.SORT, A.SUSIK_NAME

data.name: grdScPre_modifier.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.SUSIK_CODE , A.SUSIK_NAME , A.SUSIK_NAME_GANA , A.SUSIK_DETAIL_GUBUN FROM CHT0115 A ,VW_OUTSANG_SUSIK_RANK B WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.SUSIK_DETAIL_GUBUN LIKE :f_susik_detail_gubun AND ( A.SUSIK_NAME LIKE '%'||:f_susik_name||'%' OR A.SUSIK_NAME_GANA LIKE '%'||:f_susik_name||'%' ) AND NVL(A.SUSIK_DISABLE_DATE, TO_DATE('99991231', 'YYYYMMDD')) >= TRUNC(SYSDATE) -- AND B.SUSIK_CODE (+) = A.SUSIK_CODE AND B.IO_GUBUN (+) = :f_io_gubun AND B.DOCTOR (+) = :f_user_id ORDER BY NVL(B.RANK_CNT, 0) DESC, A.SORT, A.SUSIK_CODE, A.SUSIK_NAME
